## 🎨 Icon Customization

The chatbot uses SVG icons for a professional look:

### Current Icons
- **Header Icon**: Checkmark in circle (success/assistance)
- **Toggle Icon**: Chat bubble with lines (communication)
- **Send Icon**: Paper plane (send message)

### Custom Icons
You can replace any icon by modifying the SVG paths in `chatbot.js`:

```javascript
// Example: Replace with a robot icon
<svg class="chatbot-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
    <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/>
</svg>
```

